    A class to configure a Zeebe Sink Connector with sane defaults.

    The connector is designed to get complex events from a running Siddhi instace

    .

    It also holds the attribute 'mongoDB_logging' which is not a configuration property of a Zeebe Sink Connetor. 'mongoDB_logging' is a way to enable logging in a MongoDB for the events which are sent to this sink connector.

    An object of this class can be converted to a properties file for the Zeebe Sink Connector in json with the Jackson ObjectMapper.
